{{No footnotes|date=August 2013}} '''Brian Orend''' is the Director of International Studies and a professor of [[Philosophy]] at the [[University of Waterloo]] in [[Waterloo, Ontario]].
Orend's works focus on [[just war theory]] and [[human rights]]. He is most well known for his discussions of [[jus post bellum]] (justice after war), which deals with the termination phase of war.
